{"tid":2109666,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"涉掌摑警二代 警長表證成立","createTime":"2020-07-15T11:19:08.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-15T11:35:25.000Z","uid":25558,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"11a308a4e26431e7d295e079f8a68791b5821058","tid":2109666,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-15T11:19:08.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200715/5E45MFIEHU437HB7CFYVW3SNEM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200715%2F5E45MFIEHU437HB7CFYVW3SNEM%2F&d=Qf9F%2BOyPnpVTj1ufbg5Gu79EqtgOipuK5hw8%2B6jdv%2Bo%3D&h=f83db35d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200715%2F5E45MFIEHU437HB7CFYVW3SNEM%2F&h=407bee52\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200715/5E45MFIEHU437HB7CFYVW3SNEM/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n涉掌摑警二代 警長表證成立<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/MGcjfxxLL9YuPnpTI4eM0AlDGfo=/190x108/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/XZ45IJNADYH5WLT5OYOFRI4GTQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FMGcjfxxLL9YuPnpTI4eM0AlDGfo%3D%2F190x108%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FXZ45IJNADYH5WLT5OYOFRI4GTQ.jpg&h=f036c0ee&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n被告黃明偉<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】軍裝警長涉2017年執勤期間，在警車內濫用私刑三度掌摑被捕市民，他否認普通襲擊罪昨續審。警長自辯稱，當時事主雙手鎖在前面，三度將手擺近臉頰及站起，疑想逃走或施襲，他於是三度伸手撥開事主的手，其間發出「啪、啪、啪」三聲。惟裁判官陳慧敏觀看案發影片後，認為警長似用右手摑事主左臉。另一名警員亦供稱，片中傳出疑似掌摑聲前，他已用手銬將事主雙手鎖在身後。<br />\n<br />\n被告黃明偉（47歲）涉2017年4月11日在土瓜灣道與落山道交界的警車內襲擊男子李文瀚。李在庭上稱其父是退休警。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n法官睇片指動作似摑臉<br />\n<br />\n辯方質疑，。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n警員黃潔斌供稱，。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n陳官裁定案件表證成立。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n控方質疑，若事主圖在警車內起身逃走，為何被告不叫同袍合力按住，反選擇「撥開」事主的手。被。。。。。。。。。。。。。控方又指被告的撥手動作或會傷害事主。被告沉默約十秒後表示「有機會係」，並同意事前從沒要求事主放下手或坐下。案件本月21日續審。<br />\n<br />\n案件編號：KCCC2771/19"},{"pid":"7cfd82f7b655c894589548b0d0172bc293700d2b","tid":2109666,"uid":199893,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-15T11:30:06.000Z","msg":"大話連篇 垃圾狗"},{"pid":"08592fa63ed38047e953f1031b64b00331f3d95f","tid":2109666,"uid":255650,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-15T11:34:08.000Z","msg":"以為好威威，點知官位唔夠人地老豆大？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f79db526affb6d34ffb81487ac793fbe9020aba","tid":2109666,"uid":156376,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-15T11:35:25.000Z","msg":"狗咬狗骨"}]}